									<h3 class="h3_sub_title_v1">Unemployment Benefits</h3>
									<p class="text_type_v5">
										Amount of Unemployment Benefits = 50% of the average salary before retirement x number of days (maximum amount per day: KRW 43,000, minimum amount per day: 90% of the minimum wage)
									</p>
									<p class="text_type_v5 mg_t5">
										Number of days of unemployment benefits: The number of days of unemployment benefits ranges from 90 to 240, and is based on the age of the employee at the time of dismissal and the duration of the employment insurance subscription.
									</p>
								</section>
							</div>

